@page "/about"

<h2>SkyDocs by Michiel Post</h2>
<div>
    <p>
        SkyDocs is created by Michiel Post for <a href="https://gitcoin.co/hackathon/skydb/onboard" target="_blank">The SkyDB Debut</a> hackathon.<br />
        Further development is made possible by a grant from <a href="https://thegraph.com" target="_blank">The Graph</a> and <a href="https://dfinity.org" target="_blank">Dfinity Internet Computer</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
        Source code is available on <a href="https://github.com/michielpost/SkyDocs" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
    </p>

    <p>
        Features:
        <ul>
            <li>Login with your personal username and password</li>
            <li>Login with MetaMask</li>
            <li>Login with Dfinity Internet Identity</li>
            <li>See a list of your documents</li>
            <li>Screenshot preview of all documents</li>
            <li>Edit documents</li>
            <li>Delete documents</li>
            <li>Share documents (read only or with write permissions)</li>
        </ul>
    </p>

    <p>
        NOTE: All data (except preview images) stored on Sia Skynet is encrypted.
        <br />
        <br />
        SkyDocs is build with Blazor and runs on WebAssembly.
    </p>

    <p>
        @{
            string? versionHash = Program.GetVersionHash();
        }
        Version: @Program.GetVersionWithoutHash()
        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(versionHash))
        {
            <text>-</text><a href="https://github.com/michielpost/SkyDocs/tree/@versionHash" target="_blank">@versionHash</a>
        }
    </p>
</div>